        "content": "<p>You have both <code>[LinearOrder α]</code> and <code>[Preorder α]</code> and got the wrong <code>&lt;</code>. You should drop the <code>[Preorder α]</code>, it is interfering with <code>[LinearOrder α]</code>.</p>\n<p><code>[LinearOrder α]</code> means \"let there be a linear order on <code>α</code>\" and <code>[Preorder α]</code> means \"let there be a preorder on <code>α</code>\" so having both means there are now two different orders on <code>α</code> and they're both written the same but only one of them is a linear order.</p>",
